QuestData.Title: Grummle! Grummle! Grummle!
QuestData.Description: Now that grummles are rescued, we need to rescue our supplies.$b$bThe Ook of Dook is only chief because he has supplies.$b$bGo to the Dooker Dome area north west of here. Take some grummles with you. Keep them safe and get them near supply crates.$b$bGrummles know what to do from there.$b$bRabbitsfoot and I will meet you there.
QuestData.LogDescription: Lead 5 Packless Grummles to Supply Crates near the Dooker Dome.
QuestData.CompletionText: Grummles are good at carrying things.
QuestData.RewardText: Now that hozen king is going to learn why it is bad fortune to cheat grummles.
